item.title: CVE-2017-3896|2024-08-05T14:39:41.126Z -- intel -- mcafee%20agent
item.description: Unvalidated parameter vulnerability in the remote log viewing capability in Intel Security McAfee Agent 5.0.x versions prior to 5.0.4.449 allows remote attackers to pass unexpected input parameters via a URL that was not completely validated.
